# Dependencies
**/node_modules/**
/vendor/**

# Presta cache & logs (anywhere in tree, e.g. prestashop/)
**/var/cache/**
**/var/logs/**
**/app/cache/**

# Generated assets (jeśli masz build output)
**/dist/**
**/build/**
**/.parcel-cache/**
**/.vite/**
**/.next/**
**/.turbo/**
**/coverage/**

# Uploads / images / heavy binaries
**/img/**
**/download/**
**/mails/**

# Local env files
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# IDE / system
**/.idea/**
**/.vscode/**
**/.DS_Store
